+## Codecs
+
+* All devices with hardware encoding/decoding support in their stock OS MUST support hardware encoding/decoding for all codecs supported by their stock OS.
+
 ## Display
 
 * All devices with a built-in Display MUST support the Display at the same resolution and  density as the stock OS.
